    "7 In this way we expect Q to play a role similar to kappa symmetry in the Green-Schwarz superstring.",
    "8 The u(1, 1|2)1 free fields contribute c = 0, whilst the (b, c) ghost system contributes c = -26.",
    "Finally, the Z-gauging removes two bosonic degrees of freedom, contributing c = -2.",
    "This gives c = -28 overall.",
